ChangeQuery(String) - Method in class com.youtube.crash_games_cr_mc.simpleDB.query.SimpleStringDataBaseQuery
Query schematic:
update |database| |table| |conditions| |new values|
insert |database| |table| |new values|
delete |database| |table| |conditions|
create database |database|
create table |database| |table|
create column |database| |table| |column|
load |database file path|
unload |database|
save |database| |file path|
Some example queries: update main users user,str:admin darkTheme,bool:true (update the admin's dark theme setting to true) insert main users user,str:root;darkTheme,bool:false (add a new user "root" who has dark theme disabled) delete main users user,str:admin (remove the user "admin") create database main (creates the database "main") create table main users (creates the table "users" in database "main") create column main users ID (creates a new column in the table "users" in database "main") load main.db (loads a database from the file "main.db") unload main (unloads the database main; THIS DOES NOT SAVE IT) save main main.db (saves the database "main" to "main.db")
